  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>-  Manage and support in HR, office admin, sales and operations functions;</p><p>·     Oversee whole office recruitment and staff onboarding;</p><p>·     Fulfill foreign recruitment from Prior Approval application (work permit quota), work pass application and renewal, security bond, logistics to dormitory arrangements, of all related companies;</p><p>·     Payroll management ensuring timely and accurate submission, including all statutory submissions, employment income submissions, etc.;</p><p>·     Oversee and lead the sales and operations team;</p><p>·     Engage and escalate direct to clients for unresolved accounts receivables;</p><p>·     Ensure operations staff credentials and medical remain valid;</p><p>·     Ensure all company’s licensing and permit matters are in compliance;</p><p>·     Administer, review and renew all company’s insurances;</p><p>·     General support to the Director;</p><p>·     Any other ad-hoc duties assigned<br /></p><p><br />Job requirements : <br />- diploma / degree in management or related<br />- at least 3 years experience in manager and above level in any fields </p>",
